--[[
    Auto Bounty
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - Accepts ONLY bounties whose rewards include "Trait Shards" (trait rerolls)
    - Declines bounties that do NOT give trait shards
    - Runs ONE bounty active at a time
    - Detects the bounty's world, launches that Story map (configurable Act /
      Difficulty), waits for the run to clear (your units auto-fight), then
      returns to the lobby, claims the reward and accepts the next trait bounty
    - Repeats until there are no trait-reroll bounties left

    AUTO EXECUTE:
      Starting a stage teleports you to a battle place. Auto Execute uses
      queue_on_teleport to re-run this script (from SCRIPT_URL) after every
      teleport so the loop resumes automatically. Toggle it in Misc, or
      override the url with getgenv().AutoBountyScriptURL = "...".

    ANTI-AFK:
      Blocks the 20-minute idle kick (Idled hook + input nudge + disables any
      built-in AFK script). Toggle it in the Misc tab.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------]]

